Nigeria’s minister of Niger Delta Affairs, Godswill Akpabio couldn’t hide his happiness after his inauguration yesterday. The new minister of Niger Delta Affairs, Senator Godswill Akpabio has celebrated his appointment as Buhari’s Minister by dancing ‘Gbe body’, ‘Zanku’ legwork shortly after his Swearing-in. The ex-Akwa Ibom Governor failed in his bid to return as Senator. No wonder he is more than elated to be a minister. Watch video below: Ex Akwa Ibom Governor, Senator #GodswillAkpabio Dances To Celebrate His Ministerial Appointment After Failing To Return As Senator. #akpabio #APC #AkwaIbom #Minister #gbebody #zanku #zankulegwork A post shared by  TheFamousNaija (@thefamousnaija) on Aug 21, 2019 at 5:09pm PDT Source